commit.message: feat: implemented digits normalization

fix decode/encode tashkeel

- test with python2
- move it to trans.py
change version number

Add new functions

-- decode tashkeel into ascii
-- spellit:  to spell a word by letters names.
-- auocorrect: correct common typography errors
Add new function "fix_spaces" to correct spaces in joined phrases
add ordinalnumber

[trans] Add new transliteration function

In some cases, especially for identifier names, we need a plain ascii
convertion with out any symbol.
use convert(text, "arabic", "latin")
Add number to ordinal function

add normalize module
